### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/

###

### ===== AUTH =====

### Register
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Quang",
  "email": "quang@test.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "quang@test.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### Get Me (thay <TOKEN> bằng accessToken từ Login)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

###

### Test validation error (password quá ngắn)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "123"
}

###

### Test 401 (không có token)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me

###

### Test 403 (token sai)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.here

###

### ===== FOOD =====
# Lấy token từ Login rồi thay vào @token bên dưới
@token = <PASTE_TOKEN_HERE>

### Thêm food mới
POST http://localhost:3000/api/foods
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Sữa tươi",
  "quantity": 2,
  "unit": "hộp",
  "expiryDate": "2026-07-01"
}

###

### Thêm food sắp hết hạn (warning)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/foods
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Bánh mì",
  "quantity": 1,
  "unit": "ổ",
  "expiryDate": "2026-06-29"
}

###

### Thêm food đã hết hạn (expired)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/foods
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Phô mai cũ",
  "quantity": 1,
  "unit": "miếng",
  "expiryDate": "2026-06-01"
}

###

### Lấy tất cả foods
GET http://localhost:3000/api/foods
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Lấy foods theo status
GET http://localhost:3000/api/foods?status=expired
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET http://localhost:3000/api/foods?status=warning
GET http://localhost:3000/api/foods?status=warning
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Stats
GET http://localhost:3000/api/foods/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Cập nhật food (thay <FOOD_ID> bằng id từ response)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/foods/<FOOD_ID>
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "quantity": 3,
  "expiryDate": "2026-08-01"
}

###

### Xóa food
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/foods/<FOOD_ID>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

